      "name": "MAGINARI",
      "description": "MAGINARI is a curated digital exhibition platform for exclusive fashion, presenting collections by leading and emerging creative directors as cultural exhibitions rather than retail. Created by Exclamation Studios, it elevates fashion from commerce into cultural exhibition, where audiences discover, experience, collect, and participate in fashion culture. It is distinct from the fictional 'maginari' of fantasy literature and unrelated musical works of the same name.",
